OL,3,CShopkeeper found with 1,000 illegal
OL,4,Cvapes handed #180 fine
OL,6,FA shopkeeper who was found to have
OL,7,Fclose to 1,000 illegal disposable
OL,8,Fvapes on his premises has been handed
OL,9,Fa suspended sentence and a #180 fine.
OL,11,FSyed Nasir Raza Shah, 56, of Fountain
OL,12,FRoad in Stretford, was charged with
OL,13,Ffour offences after 980 illegal vapes
OL,14,Fwere seized from his shop, called
OL,15,FPound Hut, in Hazel Grove.
OL,17,FThe vapes were discovered in two
OL,18,Fseparate seizures on 5 April 2023 and
OL,19,F5 July 2023.
