OL,4,Cvapes handed #180 fine
OL,6,FMr Shah was also prosecuted in 2023 by
OL,7,FStockport Council for selling a vape
OL,8,Fto a minor, for which he was fined
OL,9,F#8,000.
OL,11,FCouncillor Dan Oliver, Cabinet Member
OL,12,Ffor Public Protection at Stockport
OL,13,FCouncil, said: "This prosecution
OL,14,Fdemonstrates our zero-tolerance
OL,15,Fapproach to the sale of illegal and
OL,16,Funsafe vaping products. These items
OL,17,Fare often aimed at younger consumers
OL,18,Fand pose serious health risks. This
OL,19,Fprosecution sends out a clear message:
OL,20,Fif you flout the law, we will
OL,21,Finvestigate and take firm action."
